<div id='communityQuestionsWithAnswers'>
<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1883380-the-reviews-beg-a-question-how-old-are">The reviews beg a question. How old are the people who are the most negative reviewers? I read the book back in 1976. I was 24. It was fascinating, abstract, picturesque and yes, random. I&#39;ll be reading this book again, this time on Audiobook. I&#39;m writing a male character who is my age looking back to that time and his point of view must be 1973 appropriate in terms of dialect and sexual morals of the day. See next.</a>
</div>
