<div id="review_587713645" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/587713645" />
    <a title="Vit Babenco" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/19283284-vit-babenco"><img alt="Vit Babenco" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1365604577p2/19283284.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/587713645?book_show_action=true">Apr 11, 2013</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Vit Babenco" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Vit Babenco" href="/user/show/19283284-vit-babenco">Vit Babenco</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Mass Market Paperback 9780553101164" href="/book/show/7573.Even_Cowgirls_Get_the_Blues">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer587713645" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer8067586073250443250"><i>Even Cowgirls Get the Blues</i> by <b>Tom Robbins</b> isn’t his best but it serves well to measure the peculiarity of epoch it tells us about.<br/><blockquote>A book no more contains reality than a clock contains time. A book may measure so-called reality as a clock measures so-called time; a book may create an illusion of reality as a clock creates an illusion of time; a book may be real, just as a clock is real…</blockquote><br/>We gravitate to illusions and so often we get caught by them and become their captives for life.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

