<span id="freeTextContainer11609930546191915585">Bah. Many people won&apos;t find this review helpful. I do care about that, but not enough to change my review, because I feel it encompasses my feelings for this book quite fully. Here it is:<br/><br/>I had to choose between continuing to read ECGTB or staring at the back of the airplane seat in front of me. <br/><br/>I chose the back of the seat.<br/><br/>Repeatedly.<br/><br/>I&apos;d read a section, and think to myself &quot;This is shit!&quot; and put it down to stare at the seat in front of me. Then I would think to myself &quot;Come on. You&apos;re on a plan</span>
